var e=JSON.parse(`[{"id":"L3_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"SOLDIOR_FLOOR_RESEARCH_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"이런 일은 처음이군요. 셰퍼드가 기절을 하다니.","JPN":"こんなことは初めてですね。シェパードが気絶するとは。","ENG":"Well, this is a first. Shepherd just fainted.","TWN":"第一次發生這種事。牧羊犬昏倒了。"},"stage":{"bg":"LAB_02","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_02","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":null,"R":null}}},{"id":"L4_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"SOLDIOR_FLOOR_RESEARCH_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"냉동고가 너무 추워서 그랬다기엔, 이전에도 곧잘 견뎌냈는데 말이죠.","JPN":"前まではよく耐えていたので、冷凍庫が寒すぎたってことはないと思いますが。","ENG":"I don't think it's because the freezer is too cold, because she had no problems before.","TWN":"是因為冰箱太冷了嗎，可是之前都沒有問題。"},"stage":{"bg":"LAB_02","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_02","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":null,"R":null}}},{"id":"L5_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"EDWIN_FLOOR_NULL_MASK","text":{"KOREA":"감기가 아니에요. 합성 시술에서 문제점을 발견했습니다.","JPN":"風邪ではありません。合成施術で、問題点を発見しました。","ENG":"She doesn't have a cold. I found a problem with the synthesizing procedure.","TWN":"不是因為感冒。我在合成手術中發現了一個問題。"},"stage":{"bg":"LAB_02","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_02","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"EDWIN_FLOOR_NULL_MASK","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L6_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"EDWIN_FLOOR_NULL_MASK","text":{"KOREA":"셰퍼드의 집속부에 모인 스프리건 인자가 계속해서 결속을 잃고 흩어지고 있어요.","JPN":"シェパードの集束部に溜まったスプリガン因子が結束を失い、ずっとバラバラな状態です。","ENG":"The Spriggan Factors gathered in Shepherd's concentration unit is losing its bond and dispersing.","TWN":"聚集在牧羊犬體內集束單元守護者因子正在失去結合並向外分散。"},"stage":{"bg":"LAB_02","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_02","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"EDWIN_FLOOR_NULL_MASK","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L7_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"SOLDIOR_FLOOR_RESEARCH_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"흠… 적합자라곤 해도 결국 사람의 심장은 나무를 완전히 대체할 수 없다는 거군요.","JPN":"ふむ……適合者だとしても、結局人間の心臓は完璧に木の代わりにはなれないということですね。","ENG":"Hmm... So even if we find a suitable candidate, the human heart is not enough to completely replace the tree.","TWN":"唔……就算再契合，人的心臟也不能完全代替樹木。"},"stage":{"bg":"LAB_02","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_02","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"EDWIN_FLOOR_NULL_MASK","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":{"char_id":"SOLDIOR_FLOOR_RESEARCH_NULL","face":"UNIT_IDLE"}}}},{"id":"L8_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"SOLDIOR_FLOOR_RESEARCH_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"셰퍼드의 심장을 뛰게 하는 스프리건 인자가 흩어지면, 셰퍼드의 생명기능도 정지할 테고요.","JPN":"シェパードの心臓を動かすスプリガン因子がバラバラになると、シェパードの生命機能も停止するはずです。","ENG":"The Spriggan Factor is what keeps Shepherd's heart beating. If it disperses, Shepherd's vital functions will also stop.","TWN":"如果讓提供牧羊犬心跳的守護者因子完全消散，牧羊犬的生命機能也會停止。"},"stage":{"bg":"LAB_02","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_02","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"EDWIN_FLOOR_NULL_MASK","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":{"char_id":"SOLDIOR_FLOOR_RESEARCH_NULL","face":"UNIT_IDLE"}}}},{"id":"L9_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"EDWIN_FLOOR_NULL_MASK","text":{"KOREA":"맞아요. 지금 당장 셰퍼드를 동면처리 하고, 너무 늦기 전에 또다른 청동나무를 찾아야 합니다.","JPN":"そのとおりです。今すぐシェパードを冬眠処理して、手遅れにならないうちに別の青銅の木を探すべきです。","ENG":"Yes. We should put Shepherd in hibernation for now and find another Bronze Tree before it's too late.","TWN":"沒錯。我們應該讓牧羊犬暫時進入冬眠狀態，並在為時已晚之前找到另一棵青銅樹。"},"stage":{"bg":"LAB_02","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_02","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"EDWIN_FLOOR_NULL_MASK","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":{"char_id":"SOLDIOR_FLOOR_RESEARCH_NULL","face":"UNIT_IDLE"}}}},{"id":"L10_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"EDWIN_FLOOR_NULL_MASK","text":{"KOREA":"그래야만 스프리건 인자를 안정시킬 수 있어요.","JPN":"でないと、スプリガン因子を安定させることはできません。","ENG":"That's the only way for us to stabilize the Spriggan Factor.","TWN":"只有這樣，守護者因子才能穩定下來。"},"stage":{"bg":"LAB_02","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_02","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"EDWIN_FLOOR_NULL_MASK","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":{"char_id":"SOLDIOR_FLOOR_RESEARCH_NULL","face":"UNIT_IDLE"}}}},{"id":"L11_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"SOLDIOR_FLOOR_RESEARCH_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"그건 곤란합니다, 박사님.","JPN":"それは困ります、博士。","ENG":"That will be difficult, Doctor.","TWN":"這很難實現，博士。"},"stage":{"bg":"LAB_02","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_02","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"EDWIN_FLOOR_NULL_MASK","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":{"char_id":"SOLDIOR_FLOOR_RESEARCH_NULL","face":"UNIT_IDLE"}}}},{"id":"L12_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"SOLDIOR_FLOOR_RESEARCH_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"또다른 청동나무를 찾는 과정이 얼마나 걸릴지 모르는 상황에서 프로젝트를 임의로 중단할 순 없습니다.","JPN":"別の青銅の木を探すのにどれくらいの時間がかかるかわからない状況で、プロジェクトを任意に中断することはできません。","ENG":"We don't know how long finding another Bronze Tree is going to take, and we can't suspend the project because of it either.","TWN":"我們不知道需要多長時間才能找到另一棵青銅樹，更別說因此而貿然停止這個項目。"},"stage":{"bg":"LAB_02","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_02","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"EDWIN_FLOOR_NULL_MASK","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":{"char_id":"SOLDIOR_FLOOR_RESEARCH_NULL","face":"UNIT_IDLE"}}}},{"id":"L13_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"EDWIN_FLOOR_NULL_MASK","text":{"KOREA":"셰퍼드가 죽으면 프로젝트도 끝장이잖습니까!","JPN":"シェパードが死んだら、プロジェクトも終わってしまうでしょう！","ENG":"But the project will be over if Shepherd dies!","TWN":"如果牧羊犬死了，這個項目就結束了！"},"stage":{"bg":"LAB_02","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_02","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"EDWIN_FLOOR_NULL_MASK","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":{"char_id":"SOLDIOR_FLOOR_RESEARCH_NULL","face":"UNIT_IDLE"}}},"sfx":"FX_CUTSCEN_NOISE_RUSTLE_04"},{"id":"L14_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"SOLDIOR_FLOOR_RESEARCH_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"그렇진 않습니다. 상부에서 오리지널을 토대로 새로운 셰퍼드를 확보하기로 결정했으니까요.","JPN":"そんなことはありません。上層部で、オリジナルを元に新たなシェパードを確保することにしましたから。","ENG":"Not quite. The higher-ups have decided to secure a new Shepherd based on the original.","TWN":"不會的。高層決定在原來這個的基礎上，培養一個新的牧羊犬。"},"stage":{"bg":"LAB_02","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_02","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"EDWIN_FLOOR_NULL_MASK","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":{"char_id":"SOLDIOR_FLOOR_RESEARCH_NULL","face":"UNIT_IDLE"}}}},{"id":"L15_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"SOLDIOR_FLOOR_RESEARCH_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"오리지널이 소실되더라도, 다른 양산기를 통해 프로젝트를 지속할 수 있을 겁니다.","JPN":"オリジナルが消えても、別の量産機を通じてプロジェクトを続行することができるはずです。","ENG":"So even if the original is lost, we can continue the project with mass-produced clones.","TWN":"這樣即使原型體損壞了，該項目也能透過量產繼續進行。"},"stage":{"bg":"LAB_02","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_02","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"EDWIN_FLOOR_NULL_MASK","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":{"char_id":"SOLDIOR_FLOOR_RESEARCH_NULL","face":"UNIT_IDLE"}}}},{"id":"L16_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"EDWIN_FLOOR_NULL_MASK","text":{"KOREA":"그게 무슨 소리죠? 아직 불완전한 객체를 벌써 양산화하다뇨?","JPN":"どういうことですか？　まだ不完全な客体をもう量産化するなんて。","ENG":"What do you mean? You're putting an incomplete unit into production?","TWN":"這是什麼意思？你們要量產一個尚未完成的試驗體？"},"stage":{"bg":"LAB_02","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_02","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"EDWIN_FLOOR_NULL_MASK","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":{"char_id":"SOLDIOR_FLOOR_RESEARCH_NULL","face":"UNIT_IDLE"}}}},{"id":"L17_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"EDWIN_FLOOR_NULL_MASK","text":{"KOREA":"설령 지금 같은 상태에서 다른 셰퍼드를 만든다고 해도 일 년을 못 버틸 겁니다! 지금처럼요!","JPN":"たとえ今のような状態で別のシェパードを作り出すとしても、1年も持たないはずです！　今回のように！","ENG":"Even if we were to make an identical Shepherd, it won't last a year! Just like now!","TWN":"即使我們再創造一個的牧羊犬，那也撐不了一年！就像現在！"},"stage":{"bg":"LAB_02","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_02","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"EDWIN_FLOOR_NULL_MASK","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":{"char_id":"SOLDIOR_FLOOR_RESEARCH_NULL","face":"UNIT_IDLE"}}}},{"id":"L18_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"SOLDIOR_FLOOR_RESEARCH_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"하지만 오리지널이 없어도 두번째, 세번째 셰퍼드를 만들어 연구를 지속할 수 있겠죠.","JPN":"ですが、オリジナルがいなくても2番目、3番目のシェパードを作って研究を続行させることは可能でしょう。","ENG":"But it will allow us to continue with our project by creating a second and third Shepherd without the original.","TWN":"但是，哪怕沒有原型，你也可以透過創造第二個或第三個牧羊犬來繼續研究。"},"stage":{"bg":"LAB_02","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_02","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"EDWIN_FLOOR_NULL_MASK","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":{"char_id":"SOLDIOR_FLOOR_RESEARCH_NULL","face":"UNIT_IDLE"}}}},{"id":"L19_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"SOLDIOR_FLOOR_RESEARCH_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"어디에 있는지 모를 새로운 청동나무를 찾아 셰퍼드의 수명을 연장시키지 않더라도 말입니다.","JPN":"どこにあるかわからない新しい青銅の木を探して、シェパードの寿命を延長させなくてもね。","ENG":"It also eliminates the need to find another god-knows-where Bronze Tree in order to extend Shepherd's life.","TWN":"也無需尋找新的青銅樹來延續牧羊犬的生命了。"},"stage":{"bg":"LAB_02","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_02","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"EDWIN_FLOOR_NULL_MASK","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":{"char_id":"SOLDIOR_FLOOR_RESEARCH_NULL","face":"UNIT_IDLE"}}}},{"id":"L20_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"EDWIN_FLOOR_NULL_MASK","text":{"KOREA":"뭐라고…?","JPN":"何だと……？","ENG":"What...?","TWN":"你、你說什麼……？"},"stage":{"bg":"LAB_02","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_02","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"EDWIN_FLOOR_NULL_MASK","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":{"char_id":"SOLDIOR_FLOOR_RESEARCH_NULL","face":"UNIT_IDLE"}}}},{"id":"L21_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"SOLDIOR_FLOOR_RESEARCH_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"프리하트 박사님의 마음을 이해하지 못하는 건 아닙니다.","JPN":"プラハト博士の気持ちはわかります。","ENG":"I understand what you're feeling, Dr. Freeheart.","TWN":"我理解普立哈特博士你的感受。"},"stage":{"bg":"LAB_02","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_02","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"EDWIN_FLOOR_NULL_MASK","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":{"char_id":"SOLDIOR_FLOOR_RESEARCH_NULL","face":"UNIT_IDLE"}}}},{"id":"L24_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"SOLDIOR_FLOOR_RESEARCH_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"하지만 저희 프로젝트에 수많은 인명이 걸려있다는 걸 잊지 마십시오.","JPN":"ですが、このプロジェクトに数多くの人命がかかっているということをお忘れなく。","ENG":"But don't forget that many lives are at stake in our project.","TWN":"但不要忘記，我們的項目事關許多人的生命。"},"stage":{"bg":"LAB_02","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_02","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"EDWIN_FLOOR_NULL_MASK","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":{"char_id":"SOLDIOR_FLOOR_RESEARCH_NULL","face":"UNIT_IDLE"}}}},{"id":"L27_1","type":"dialog","speaker":null,"text":{"KOREA":"그 말을 듣고서야 난 깨달았어. 정말 순진했지.","JPN":"その言葉を聞いて僕は気付いた。本当に純粋だった。","ENG":"I realized when I heard those words. I was naive.","TWN":"聽到那句話後，我才恍然大悟。我真的太天真了。"},"stage":{"bg":"LAB","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_02","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":null,"R":null}},"sfx":"FX_CUTSCEN_PHONE"},{"id":"L28_1","type":"dialog","speaker":null,"text":{"KOREA":"나에겐 마지막 희망이었던 것이, 그들에겐 한낱 대체가능한 수단이었을 뿐인 거야.","JPN":"僕には最後の希望だったものが、彼らにはただ代替可能な手段であるだけだったんだ。","ENG":"What was to me my last hope was just another means to an end for them.","TWN":"我最後的希望，對他們來說只是不過是一種可以替代的手段罷了。"},"stage":{"bg":"LAB","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_02","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":null,"R":null}}},{"id":"L31_1","type":"dialog","speaker":null,"text":{"KOREA":"하지만 그게 전부가 아니었어.","JPN":"でも、それだけじゃなかった。","ENG":"But that wasn't everything.","TWN":"但這還不是全部。"},"stage":{"bg":"BLACK","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_02","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":null,"R":null}}},{"id":"L32_1","type":"dialog","speaker":null,"text":{"KOREA":"프로젝트 셰퍼드.","JPN":"プロジェクト・シェパード。","ENG":"Project Shepherd.","TWN":"牧羊人計畫。"},"stage":{"bg":"BLACK","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_02","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":null,"R":null}}},{"id":"L33_1","type":"dialog","speaker":null,"text":{"KOREA":"그 연구의 내막을 파고들수록, 인류를 구한다는 취지와는 거리가 멀어 보였거든.","JPN":"その研究の内部事情を知れば知るほど、人類救済という趣旨とはほど遠く思えたんだ。","ENG":"As I delved deeper into its research, I found that their purpose was far from saving humanity.","TWN":"我越深入研究這個項目的內幕，它似乎離拯救人類的目的就越遠。"},"stage":{"bg":"BLACK","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_02","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":null,"R":null}}},{"id":"L38_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"EDWIN_FLOOR_NULL_MASK","text":{"KOREA":"대체 언제까지 셰퍼드가 합성 침식체들을 통제해야 하는 겁니까?","JPN":"いったいいつまでシェパードに合成侵食体たちのコントロールをさせるつもりですか？","ENG":"How long will Shepherd have to control these synthetic C.O.s.?","TWN":"牧羊犬需要控制合成侵蝕體多久？"},"stage":{"bg":"CORRIDOR","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_02","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"EDWIN_FLOOR_NULL_MASK","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L39_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"EDWIN_FLOOR_NULL_MASK","text":{"KOREA":"이런 실험에 무슨 의미가 있죠?","JPN":"こんな実験に何の意味があるんですか？","ENG":"What's the point of all these tests?","TWN":"這些實驗的意義在哪裡？"},"stage":{"bg":"CORRIDOR","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_02","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"EDWIN_FLOOR_NULL_MASK","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":null}},"sfx":"FX_CUTSCEN_PHONE"},{"id":"L40_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"RESEARCHER_FLOOR_UNION_ASSIST","text":{"KOREA":"스프리건 인자의 통제력이 어디까지 영향을 미치는지 그 한계를 시험하는 겁니다.","JPN":"スプリガン因子のコントロール力がどこまで影響するか、その限界を実験するのです。","ENG":"We are testing the limits of the Spriggan Factor's influence.","TWN":"我們正在測試守護者因子的控制極限。"},"stage":{"bg":"CORRIDOR","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_02","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":{"char_id":"RESEARCHER_FLOOR_UNION_ASSIST","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"C":{"char_id":"EDWIN_FLOOR_NULL_MASK","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L41_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"RESEARCHER_FLOOR_UNION_ASSIST","text":{"KOREA":"궁극적으로는 일반 침식체 뿐만 아니라, 그 상위 수준의 존재를 통제하는 게 목표니까요.","JPN":"最終的には一般侵食体だけじゃなくて、その上位クラスの存在をコントロールすることが目標ですから。","ENG":"Our goal is to ultimately be able to control the higher-grade C.O.s other than just normal ones.","TWN":"最終的目標不僅是控制一般的侵蝕體，還包括更高層次的生命體。"},"stage":{"bg":"CORRIDOR","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_02","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":{"char_id":"RESEARCHER_FLOOR_UNION_ASSIST","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"C":{"char_id":"EDWIN_FLOOR_NULL_MASK","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L42_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"RESEARCHER_FLOOR_UNION_ASSIST","text":{"KOREA":"박사님도 아시겠지만, 인류의 적은 침식체 뿐만이 아니잖아요?","JPN":"博士もご存知のように、人類の敵は侵食体だけではないでしょう？","ENG":"As you know, Doctor, C.O.s aren't the only enemy of humanity.","TWN":"博士你應該知道，人類的敵人不僅僅是侵蝕體，對吧？"},"stage":{"bg":"CORRIDOR","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_02","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":{"char_id":"RESEARCHER_FLOOR_UNION_ASSIST","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"C":{"char_id":"EDWIN_FLOOR_NULL_MASK","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L43_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"EDWIN_FLOOR_NULL_MASK","text":{"KOREA":"설마… 그림자를 말하는 겁니까?","JPN":"まさか……シャドウのことですか？","ENG":"Are you... talking about Shadows?","TWN":"你難道……是說在暗影嗎？"},"stage":{"bg":"CORRIDOR","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_02","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":{"char_id":"RESEARCHER_FLOOR_UNION_ASSIST","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"C":{"char_id":"EDWIN_FLOOR_NULL_MASK","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L44_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"EDWIN_FLOOR_NULL_MASK","text":{"KOREA":"셰퍼드 앞에 그림자를 내놓을 작정인 건가요?","JPN":"シェパードの前に、シャドウを出すつもりなんですか？","ENG":"You're going to put Shepherd against a Shadow?","TWN":"你們打算讓牧羊犬直接面對暗影嗎？"},"stage":{"bg":"CORRIDOR","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_02","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":{"char_id":"RESEARCHER_FLOOR_UNION_ASSIST","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"C":{"char_id":"EDWIN_FLOOR_NULL_MASK","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L45_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"RESEARCHER_FLOOR_UNION_ASSIST","text":{"KOREA":"이미 다른 팀에서 러처의 사전 준비를 마쳤다고 상부에 보고했어요.","JPN":"すでに他のチームでラッチャーの事前準備が終わったと上層部に報告しました。","ENG":"The higher-ups have already received reports that the other teams have completed preparations for Lurcher.","TWN":"上級已經收到報告了，另一個團隊已經完成了獵犬的準備工作。"},"stage":{"bg":"CORRIDOR","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_02","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":{"char_id":"RESEARCHER_FLOOR_UNION_ASSIST","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"C":{"char_id":"EDWIN_FLOOR_NULL_MASK","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L46_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"RESEARCHER_FLOOR_UNION_ASSIST","text":{"KOREA":"조만간 다음 실험 지시가 내려올 겁니다.","JPN":"そのうち次の実験指示が出るでしょう。","ENG":"It won't be long before orders to conduct the following test will come in.","TWN":"下一個實驗指示即將發佈。"},"stage":{"bg":"CORRIDOR","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_02","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":{"char_id":"RESEARCHER_FLOOR_UNION_ASSIST","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"C":{"char_id":"EDWIN_FLOOR_NULL_MASK","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L47_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"EDWIN_FLOOR_NULL_MASK","text":{"KOREA":"…….","JPN":"……","ENG":"...","TWN":"……"},"stage":{"bg":"CORRIDOR","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_02","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":{"char_id":"RESEARCHER_FLOOR_UNION_ASSIST","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"C":{"char_id":"EDWIN_FLOOR_NULL_MASK","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L50_1","type":"dialog","speaker":null,"text":{"KOREA":"러처는 살아 움직이는 기계였어.","JPN":"ラッチャーは生きる機械だった。","ENG":"Lurcher was a living machine.","TWN":"獵犬是一台有生命的機器。"},"stage":{"bg":"BLACK","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_02","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":null,"R":null}}},{"id":"L1_1","type":"dialog","speaker":null,"text":{"KOREA":"셰퍼드와 다른 점이 있다면, 그건 그림자 파편을 억제기로 예속시켜 동력중추로 삼았다는 거지.","JPN":"シェパードと異なる点は、影の破片を抑制機に服従させて動力の中枢にしたということ。","ENG":"If there was one thing different than Shepherd, it used a Shadow Fragment as a power source in its inhibitor.","TWN":"與牧羊犬不同的是，它使用暗影碎片作為它的動力中樞。"},"stage":{"bg":"BLACK","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_02","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":null,"R":null}}},{"id":"L2_1","type":"dialog","speaker":null,"text":{"KOREA":"그래. 기계의 탈을 뒤집어쓴 그림자. 놈들은 실험이랍시고 자기들 손으로 그런 괴물을 만들고 있었던 거야.","JPN":"そう。機械の皮を被ったシャドウ。やつらは実験という名目で、自らそんな化け物を作り出していたんだ。","ENG":"Yeah. It was a Shadow disguised as a machine. They created a monster with their own hands for their experiments.","TWN":"沒錯。偽裝成機器的暗影。那群人為了這個實驗，用自己的雙手創造了這樣一個怪物。"},"stage":{"bg":"BLACK","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_02","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":null,"R":null}}},{"id":"L6_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"RESEARCHER_FLOOR_UNION_ASSIST","text":{"KOREA":"코드명 러처. 5차 통제 실험 결과.","JPN":"コードネーム、ラッチャー。第5次コントロール実験の結果。","ENG":"Codename Lurcher. Control experiment No. 5 results.","TWN":"代號：獵犬。第五次對照實驗的結果。"},"stage":{"bg":"CORRIDOR","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_02","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"DINO_RAS_NULL_ONLY","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":null}},"sfx":"TYPING_LOOP"},{"id":"L7_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"RESEARCHER_FLOOR_UNION_ASSIST","text":{"KOREA":"셰퍼드의 통제 영향으로 잠시 물러났지만, 20초만에 극복하고 물리력으로 탈출을 시도.","JPN":"シェパードのコントロールにより、しばらく退かせていたが、たったの20秒で克服し、物理的な力を使って脱出未遂。","ENG":"It retreated for a moment due to Shepherd's controlling influence, but overcame it after 20 seconds and tried to escape.","TWN":"因受牧羊犬控制力的影響，暫時後退，但威懾效果僅維持了二十秒，隨後試圖用物理力量逃脫。"},"stage":{"bg":"CORRIDOR","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_02","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"DINO_RAS_NULL_ONLY","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":null}},"sfx":"TYPING_LOOP"},{"id":"L8_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"RESEARCHER_FLOOR_UNION_ASSIST","text":{"KOREA":"이번에도 실패입니다.","JPN":"今回も失敗です。","ENG":"Test failed.","TWN":"這次又失敗了。"},"stage":{"bg":"CORRIDOR","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_02","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"DINO_RAS_NULL_ONLY","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":null}},"sfx":"FX_CUTSCEN_NOISE"},{"id":"L9_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"EDWIN_FLOOR_NULL_MASK","text":{"KOREA":"실험을 거듭할 때마다 녀석이 스프리건 인자의 통제를 극복하는 주기가 짧아지고 있어요.","JPN":"実験を重ねるたびに、やつがスプリガン因子のコントロールを克服する周期が短くなってます。","ENG":"The more tests we run, the Spriggan Factor's influence seems to be getting shorter.","TWN":"每進行一次實驗，它被守護者因子控制的時間就會變得更短。"},"stage":{"bg":"CORRIDOR","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_02","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"EDWIN_FLOOR_NULL_MASK","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L10_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"EDWIN_FLOOR_NULL_MASK","text":{"KOREA":"더 이상 실험을 진행했다간… 셰퍼드가 위험합니다.","JPN":"これ以上実験を進めると……シェパードが危険です。","ENG":"If we conduct any more tests... Shepherd will be in danger.","TWN":"如果繼續進行實驗的話……牧羊犬會有危險。"},"stage":{"bg":"CORRIDOR","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_02","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"EDWIN_FLOOR_NULL_MASK","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L11_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"RESEARCHER_FLOOR_UNION_ASSIST","text":{"KOREA":"저 야수 한 마리에 투자한 비용이 어느 정도인지를 생각해보면 감수할만한 희생이죠.","JPN":"あの野獣一匹に投資した費用がいくらか考えてみると、仕方ない犠牲ですよ。","ENG":"If you consider how much money we invested into creating that beast, it's a small price to pay.","TWN":"想一想我們在這頭野獸身上投入了多少資金，這是一個值得做出的犧牲。"},"stage":{"bg":"CORRIDOR","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_02","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"EDWIN_FLOOR_NULL_MASK","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":{"char_id":"RESEARCHER_FLOOR_UNION_ASSIST","face":"UNIT_IDLE"}}}},{"id":"L12_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"RESEARCHER_FLOOR_UNION_ASSIST","text":{"KOREA":"다음 통제 실험에서도 진전이 없다면 셰퍼드를 한층 더 개조해보는 것도 방법이겠네요.","JPN":"次の統制実験でも進展がないなら、シェパードを改造してみるのもいいですね。","ENG":"If there are no improvements in the next experiment, we will have to consider modifying Shepherd further.","TWN":"如果下次對照實驗還沒有進展，我們可能就需要考慮進一步改造牧羊犬了。"},"stage":{"bg":"CORRIDOR","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_02","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"EDWIN_FLOOR_NULL_MASK","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":{"char_id":"RESEARCHER_FLOOR_UNION_ASSIST","face":"UNIT_IDLE"}}}},{"id":"L13_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"EDWIN_FLOOR_NULL_MASK","text":{"KOREA":"…….","JPN":"……","ENG":"...","TWN":"……"},"stage":{"bg":"CORRIDOR","bgm":"CUTSCENE_TALK_02","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"EDWIN_FLOOR_NULL_MASK","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":{"char_id":"RESEARCHER_FLOOR_UNION_ASSIST","face":"UNIT_IDLE"}}}},{"id":"L16_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"SPIRIT_RAS_NULL_ONLY","text":{"KOREA":"러처, 많이 아파했어.","JPN":"ラッチャー、本当に苦しんでた。","ENG":"Lurcher was in a lot of pain.","TWN":"獵犬，你很痛苦。"},"stage":{"bg":"WAREHOUSE_02","bgm":"CUTSCENE_FLASHBACK","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"SPIRIT_RAS_NULL_ONLY","face":"UNIT_DESPAIR"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L17_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"SPIRIT_RAS_NULL_ONLY","text":{"KOREA":"겁주려고 하면, 이제 화내요.","JPN":"怖がらせようとすると、怒っちゃうんだ。","ENG":"If Shepherd tries to scare him, he gets mad.","TWN":"嚇唬你，你會生氣吧。"},"stage":{"bg":"WAREHOUSE_02","bgm":"CUTSCENE_FLASHBACK","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"SPIRIT_RAS_NULL_ONLY","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L18_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"EDWIN_FLOOR_NULL_MASK","text":{"KOREA":"미안하구나. 너한테 몹쓸 일을 겪게 해서.","JPN":"ごめんな。君にこんな経験させて。","ENG":"I'm sorry for making you go through all this.","TWN":"對不起。讓你經歷了可怕的事情。"},"stage":{"bg":"WAREHOUSE_02","bgm":"CUTSCENE_FLASHBACK","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"EDWIN_FLOOR_NULL_MASK","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L19_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"SPIRIT_RAS_NULL_ONLY","text":{"KOREA":"으응, 난 괜찮아요.","JPN":"ううん、シェパードは大丈夫。","ENG":"No. Shepherd is okay.","TWN":"嗯，牧羊犬很好。"},"stage":{"bg":"WAREHOUSE_02","bgm":"CUTSCENE_FLASHBACK","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"SPIRIT_RAS_NULL_ONLY","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L21_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"SPIRIT_RAS_NULL_ONLY","text":{"KOREA":"얼음- 주세요.","JPN":"氷、ちょうだい。","ENG":"Please give Shepherd ice.","TWN":"請給我——冰塊。"},"stage":{"bg":"WAREHOUSE_02","bgm":"CUTSCENE_FLASHBACK","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":{"char_id":"EDWIN_FLOOR_NULL_MASK","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"C":null,"R":{"char_id":"SPIRIT_RAS_NULL_ONLY","face":"UNIT_PRIDE"}}}},{"id":"L22_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"EDWIN_FLOOR_NULL_MASK","text":{"KOREA":"하하, 셰퍼드는 차가운 걸 참 좋아하네.","JPN":"はは、シェパードは冷たいものが本当好きだな。","ENG":"Haha. You really like cold things, don't you, Shepherd?","TWN":"呵呵，牧羊犬真的很喜歡涼的東西。"},"stage":{"bg":"WAREHOUSE_02","bgm":"CUTSCENE_FLASHBACK","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":{"char_id":"EDWIN_FLOOR_NULL_MASK","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"C":null,"R":{"char_id":"SPIRIT_RAS_NULL_ONLY","face":"UNIT_PRIDE"}}}},{"id":"L23_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"EDWIN_FLOOR_NULL_MASK","text":{"KOREA":"겨울에 태어나서 그런가?","JPN":"冬に生まれたからか？","ENG":"Is it because you were born in winter?","TWN":"是因為你出生在冬天嗎？"},"stage":{"bg":"WAREHOUSE_02","bgm":"CUTSCENE_FLASHBACK","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":{"char_id":"EDWIN_FLOOR_NULL_MASK","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"C":null,"R":{"char_id":"SPIRIT_RAS_NULL_ONLY","face":"UNIT_PRIDE"}}}},{"id":"L24_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"SPIRIT_RAS_NULL_ONLY","text":{"KOREA":"겨울…? 그게 뭐야?","JPN":"冬……？　それは何？","ENG":"Winter...? What's that?","TWN":"冬天……？那是什麼？"},"stage":{"bg":"WAREHOUSE_02","bgm":"CUTSCENE_FLASHBACK","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":{"char_id":"EDWIN_FLOOR_NULL_MASK","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"C":null,"R":{"char_id":"SPIRIT_RAS_NULL_ONLY","face":"UNIT_HATE"}}}},{"id":"L25_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"EDWIN_FLOOR_NULL_MASK","text":{"KOREA":"겨울은 현실세계의 계절 중 하나란다. 차가운 바람이 불고, 하늘에선 작은 얼음 결정이 내리지.","JPN":"冬はノーマルサイドの季節の一つだよ。冷たい風が吹いて、空からは小さな氷の結晶が降ってくる。","ENG":"It's one of the seasons in the Normalside. It's when cold winds blow and tiny pieces of ice fall from the sky.","TWN":"冬天是現實世界的季節之一。一陣冷風吹過，天空中就會下起小小的冰晶。"},"stage":{"bg":"WAREHOUSE_02","bgm":"CUTSCENE_FLASHBACK","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":{"char_id":"EDWIN_FLOOR_NULL_MASK","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"C":null,"R":{"char_id":"SPIRIT_RAS_NULL_ONLY","face":"UNIT_HATE"}}}},{"id":"L26_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"SPIRIT_RAS_NULL_ONLY","text":{"KOREA":"…….","JPN":"……","ENG":"...","TWN":"……"},"stage":{"bg":"WAREHOUSE_02","bgm":"CUTSCENE_FLASHBACK","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":{"char_id":"EDWIN_FLOOR_NULL_MASK","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"C":null,"R":{"char_id":"SPIRIT_RAS_NULL_ONLY","face":"UNIT_SURPRISE"}}}},{"id":"L27_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"SPIRIT_RAS_NULL_ONLY","text":{"KOREA":"셰퍼드, 겨울 보고 싶어. 하늘도 궁금해요.","JPN":"シェパード、冬を見たい。空も気になる。","ENG":"Shepherd wants to see winter and the sky.","TWN":"牧羊犬想看看冬天，也想看看天空。"},"stage":{"bg":"WAREHOUSE_02","bgm":"CUTSCENE_FLASHBACK","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":{"char_id":"EDWIN_FLOOR_NULL_MASK","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"C":{"char_id":"SPIRIT_RAS_NULL_ONLY","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":null}},"sfx":"FX_CUTSCEN_NOISE_RUSTLE_04"},{"id":"L28_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"EDWIN_FLOOR_NULL_MASK","text":{"KOREA":"그래… 곧 보게 해줄게.","JPN":"ああ……もうすぐ見させてあげるよ。","ENG":"Sure... You'll see them soon.","TWN":"當然……很快就能讓你看到了。"},"stage":{"bg":"WAREHOUSE_02","bgm":"CUTSCENE_FLASHBACK","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":{"char_id":"EDWIN_FLOOR_NULL_MASK","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"C":{"char_id":"SPIRIT_RAS_NULL_ONLY","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L29_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"EDWIN_FLOOR_NULL_MASK","text":{"KOREA":"그러니 셰퍼드, 얼음 먹으면서 잘 들으렴.","JPN":"だからシェパード、氷を食べながらよく聞きなさい。","ENG":"Anyway, Shepherd, listen carefully as you eat ice.","TWN":"牧羊犬，你吃著冰，仔細聽我說。"},"stage":{"bg":"WAREHOUSE_02","bgm":"CUTSCENE_FLASHBACK","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":{"char_id":"EDWIN_FLOOR_NULL_MASK","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"C":{"char_id":"SPIRIT_RAS_NULL_ONLY","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L30_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"EDWIN_FLOOR_NULL_MASK","text":{"KOREA":"지금부터 하는 얘긴, 우리 둘만의 비밀이야.","JPN":"今からの話は、僕たちだけの秘密だぞ。","ENG":"What I'm going to say now is our little secret.","TWN":"從現在開始，我要說的話是我們之間的秘密。"},"stage":{"bg":"WAREHOUSE_02","bgm":"CUTSCENE_FLASHBACK","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":{"char_id":"EDWIN_FLOOR_NULL_MASK","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"C":{"char_id":"SPIRIT_RAS_NULL_ONLY","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L31_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"SPIRIT_RAS_NULL_ONLY","text":{"KOREA":"…응.","JPN":"……うん。","ENG":"...Okay.","TWN":"……好的。"},"stage":{"bg":"WAREHOUSE_02","bgm":"CUTSCENE_FLASHBACK","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":{"char_id":"EDWIN_FLOOR_NULL_MASK","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"C":{"char_id":"SPIRIT_RAS_NULL_ONLY","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L34_1","type":"dialog","speaker":null,"text":{"KOREA":"셰퍼드를 구하려면, 가장 먼저 이 시설에서 벗어나야 했어.","JPN":"シェパードを救うためには、まずこの施設から出る必要があった。","ENG":"In order to save Shepherd, the first thing was to get out of this facility.","TWN":"為了挽救牧羊犬，我們必須先離開這個設施。"},"stage":{"bg":"BLACK","bgm":"CUTSCENE_FLASHBACK","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":null,"R":null}}},{"id":"L35_1","type":"dialog","speaker":null,"text":{"KOREA":"탈출은 순조로웠지. 러처가 실험도중에 폭주하면서 계획을 실행에 옮길 기회가 생겼거든.","JPN":"脱出は順調だった。ラッチャーが実験の途中に暴走して、計画を実行するチャンスができたから。","ENG":"Escaping was easy enough, as when Lurcher started running amok during one of the experiments, it gave us enough time to put our plan into action.","TWN":"逃亡計畫很簡單。當獵犬在實驗過程中失控時，就是我們的機會。"},"stage":{"bg":"BLACK","bgm":"CUTSCENE_FLASHBACK","filter":"NCFT_NORMAL","slots":{"L":null,"C":null,"R":null}}},{"id":"L37_1","type":"dialog","speaker":null,"text":{"KOREA":"하지만 현실의 문턱까지 다다르고나서야 알게 됐어.","JPN":"しかし、ノーマルサイドの入口まで到着して気付いた。","ENG":"But it wasn't until I reached the threshold of the Normalside that I realized it.","TWN":"但直到我到達現實的門檻時才意識到。"},"stage":{"bg":"LIFT","bgm":"CUTSCENE_FLASHBACK","filter":"NCFT_SEPIA","slots":{"L":null,"C":null,"R":null}}},{"id":"L38_1","type":"dialog","speaker":null,"text":{"KOREA":"이면세계에 존재하는 에너지를 토대로 생명을 연장한 셰퍼드의 몸은 이미 현실의 부하를 견딜 수 있는 상태가 아니었던 거야.","JPN":"裏世界に存在するエネルギーを元に命を延長したシェパードの体は、すでにノーマルサイドの負荷に耐えられる状態じゃなかったんだ。","ENG":"Shepherd's lifespan was only extended by the energy existing in the Counterside. And that her body wasn't in a state to endure the Normalside.","TWN":"牧羊犬的身體，依靠異界的能量延長了生命，已經無法承受現實的負荷了。"},"stage":{"bg":"LIFT","bgm":"CUTSCENE_FLASHBACK","filter":"NCFT_SEPIA","slots":{"L":null,"C":null,"R":null}}},{"id":"L41_1","type":"dialog","speaker":null,"text":{"KOREA":"난 그 아이를 시설에 남겨둔 채, 북방합의체의 추격을 피하며 온 이면세계를 탐험했어.","JPN":"僕はあの子を施設に残しておいたまま、北方合意体の追撃をまいて全裏世界を探検した。","ENG":"I left that child back at the facility and explored the Counterside while avoiding the pursuit of the Northern Union.","TWN":"我把那個孩子留在了設施裡，一邊躲避北方和議會的追捕，一邊探索整個異界。"},"stage":{"bg":"COUNTERSIDE_AURORA_02","bgm":"CUTSCENE_FLASHBACK","filter":"NCFT_SEPIA","slots":{"L":null,"C":null,"R":null}}},{"id":"L42_1","type":"dialog","speaker":null,"text":{"KOREA":"그 아이의 영혼을 지켜줄 새로운 청동나무를 찾을 때까지.","JPN":"あの子の魂を守ってくれる、新しい青銅の木を見つけるまで。","ENG":"Until I found a new Bronze Tree that could protect that child's soul.","TWN":"直到找到一棵新的青銅樹來保護孩子的靈魂。"},"stage":{"bg":"COUNTERSIDE_AURORA_02","bgm":"CUTSCENE_FLASHBACK","filter":"NCFT_SEPIA","slots":{"L":null,"C":null,"R":null}}}]`);export{e as default};